comment_data.body: There's likely a fix we can do the the build system here; perhaps the extension now exists in the Dart plugin for 2017.3, and we can now include the class?
Deleting https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/blob/master/product-matrix.json#L11 does seem to fix this.
